        "description": "Bench measurements were collected across two independent laboratories using production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs. Specimens were drawn from standard production inventory and tested under the ASTM F1717 loading configuration. Data collection was integrated into ongoing characterization activities; no prospective randomisation or environmental lockdown was implemented. Operator technique and ambient conditions were recorded but not controlled to fixed target values. The dataset is treated as a comprehensive observational record of construct mechanical response under the ASTM F1717 protocol.",
